query:
SELECT 
  sp.id,
  sp.tenantId,
  l.code AS endereco,
  p.name AS produto,
  p.sku,
  sp.internalCode AS codigoInterno,
  sp.quantity AS quantidade,
  sp.fractionalAvailable AS fracionadoDisponivel,
  sp.createdAt
FROM stockPositions sp
JOIN locations l ON sp.locationId = l.id
JOIN products p ON sp.productId = p.id
WHERE sp.tenantId = 1
ORDER BY l.code, p.name, sp.internalCode;
